data.description: Beautifully renovated single-story home boasts fresh neutral paint, all new wood-type flooring, recessed lighting, ceiling fans in the bedrooms, updated hardware, and all granite countertops! Inside, you'll find a spacious and open floor plan great for entertaining with a kitchen that boasts a large breakfast bar island, subway tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances! The bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled, the bedrooms have new carpet, and the utility room in-house leads to the huge, versatile converted garage space! There's plenty of room on the property for parking, plus the large backyard with a covered patio. Zoned to Hull-Daisetta ISD, this community offers a charming & serene escape for those seeking a more relaxed way of life. The town is surrounded by lush forests & scenic landscapes, making it a paradise for outdoor enthusiasts. Proximity to FM-770!
